OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy start this morning
OL,6,Fwith the odd light shower in the
OL,7,Fsouthwest. Otherwise it will be a dry
OL,8,Fday with cloud breaking to give some
OL,9,Fsunshine this afternoon.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FThis evening will be dry with
OL,12,Fcloud spreading inland across the
OL,13,Feast. Then the rest of the night will
OL,14,Fbe dry and cloudy but remaining clear
OL,15,Facross Dumfries and Galloway.
OL,16,
OL,17,CWednesday:FA dry day. Overnight cloud
OL,18,Fwill gradually lift and break to allow
OL,19,Fsome sunny intervals by afternoon, but
OL,20,Fmay linger along the east coast. Warm
OL,21,Fin the southwest, cooler elsewhere.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
