OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FDry
OL,6,Fand settled. Overnight low cloud will
OL,7,Fmostly burn off through the mornings
OL,8,Fbut may linger around the east coast.
OL,9,FWarm in the sunshine. Patchy overnight
OL,10,Ffrost.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
